year ago the typical home in the west sold for 122300 in 
november up 6 percent from a year ago 
homes in the south sold for 80300 in november an increase of 
14 percent from a year earlier while the midwest remained the 
least expensive housing area at 66700 an increase of 36 percent 
from a year ago 
