the aircraft plan to send the metal flap that peeled off the 
fuselage to the agencys washington dc laboratory for testing 
itll go back to our laboratory in washington our 
metallurgical lab and theyll use an electron microscope to 
pinpoint the type of failures on the metal itself ntsb air safety 
